content.rendered: Flexible roll format holds its shape and performs well for a number of dental procedures. Suitable for sensitive patients due to easy removal and minimal irritation.

excerpt.rendered:
– Soft and pliable, made from 100% cotton.
– Highly absorbent and maintain their shape during use.
– Latex and chlorine free.
